These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: apricot, lettuce
1. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Food   | apricot | lettuce |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, crime
1. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | crime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, disco
1. the fan of electronic is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | electronic |

 #################################

 
